column8: Keel paint in very poor condition.
Paint missing in patches around the hull.
Replaced shaft anodes. Paint missing along waterline and large areas of keel where rust is prominent.
Shaft anodes absent. Will procure and replace post-haste!
Just a quick knocking of if the big stuff so you’ll have good maneuverability and won’t be charged excessive growth fees by the yard. Have a great haulout!
